Feline::

She wiped her chrome face plates off with her chrome hands. "I got 
bit by a spider of some kind.  After the bite, that's when I started 
loosing my nice leopard pelt."  She lowered her head,"I wasn't 
programmed to handle situations like this. What am I going to do?"
Then the idea struck her. She asked,"UH, where are you going to take 
me to get fixed up?  Who are you? I don't want to walk into a death 
trap. Not after..after this."  She covered her face again and cried. 
Her chrome body, still slender and cat like, shined and reflected the 
light coming in from the windows.  It looked like a crystal prysm was 
in the window as the light and rainbows danced around inside the 
shuttle.  She tried to regain her composure and wiped her face with 
her hands. "Now what do we do?"
